reviews.text: Good Thai place. Big menu and all freshly made. Tiny seats. Helpful and quality service. The seafood coconut meal is very good. Recommended. Super clean toilets are a bonus too. Was five star but 20% service charge. Not made clear

Pretty decent Thai food at reasonable prices. There is a good menu selection to cater for different people and tastes. It's in a convenient location not to far from everything. It's a popular eatery with the locals for their friendly staff.
Cheap and delicious Thai Restaurant with tons of menu options. $43 Simple lunch set with takeaway as well. Even let me use my own containers... We frequent this place often.
Decent Thai food with pleasant staff; the only negative was my mango smoothie lacked taste
